"ngram\": \"Christians\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics has drawn significant backlash for its depiction of Leonardo da Vinci's painting \\\"The Last Supper\\\" with a \\\"drag queen\\\" performance, which many view as disrespectful to religious beliefs.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 0.9999999996689439, \"rank\": 3.310766065869911e-10, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"significant backlash\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"its depiction\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"drag queen\\\" performance\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"religious beliefs\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vakhtang Kipshidze, the deputy chairman of the Russian Orthodox Church's Synodal Department for Church Relations with Society and the Media, expressed outrage over a performance during the ceremony that depicted the \\\"Last Supper\\\" with a drag queen.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vakhtang_VI_of_Kartli\", \"score\": 0.7760630793381748, \"rank\": 0.276316231128285, \"text\": \"Vakhtang\", \